*Snow Tech's eye lids flutter and open. He groans and props his head off the 
ground with his elbows, and looks around. He catiously gets up, aware he 
could get caught, but knowing he could get caught if he just stayed there. 
When he doesn't see anything or anyone, he stands totally on both his feet, 
hoping that he hadn't broken anything important. When he checked himself 
over and found almost no damage, except for some scratches and occasional 
bruise or two.
He looks at the sky and finds he had been out for at least two or more 
hours. He hoped that Shadow Cat had found her way out of the Alien bots 
grasps and had gotten to saftey. He had the first, he wasn't caught, but he 
was still vulnrable, so was not safe. He sighed and began to follow the 
large trail made by the larger aliens back to the battle feild....*
